HEADWORD: Controversial
<hw>Con`tro*ver"sial</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[Cf. LL.
<ets>controversialis</ets>.]</ety> <def>Relating to, or consisting of,
controversy; disputatious; polemical; <as>as, <ex>controversial</ex>
divinity</as>.</def></p>

<p><-- 2. arousing controversy; not viewed similarly by everyone.
-->⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Whole libraries of <qex>controversial</qex> books.</q>
